lead_paragraph: Players from a top Argentine soccer team received emergency treatment after their bus crashed and overturned in Venezuela following a match in the Copa Libertadores.

headline.main: No Serious Injuries After Bus Carrying Argentine Soccer Team Crashes

snippet: Players from a top Argentine soccer team received emergency treatment after their bus crashed and overturned in Venezuela following a match in the Copa Libertadores.
abstract: Argentine soccer team Huracan, traveling by bus to airport after defeating Caracas FC, is involved in crash; no serious injuries are reported.
